AHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BA%A1c-th%E1%BA%A7n-ph%C3%BA/poem-ylYQnboi4bp_70hzYu0a0Q">Lạc thần phú - 洛神賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%C3%ADch-m%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%C6%A1n-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-0FIQ5x0Bql85s2IQx0Da6A">Tích mẫu đơn hoa kỳ 2 - 惜牡丹花其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-ph%C3%B2-m%C3%A3-tr%C3%AC-%C4%91%C3%A0i-h%E1%BB%89-ng%E1%BB%99-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-qu%E1%BA%A3ng-v%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-%E1%BA%A9m/poem-DcnRo0aTj__LZxuRq21gDA">Trịnh phò mã trì đài hỉ ngộ Trịnh quảng văn đồng ẩm - 鄭駙馬池臺喜遇鄭廣文同飲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/V%E1%BB%8Dng-nguy%E1%BB%87t-ho%C3%A0i-vi%E1%BB%85n/poem-teJwaO1MY5_ayICOVHrqHg">Vọng nguyệt hoài viễn - 望月懷遠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/author-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Trương Cửu Linh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
